{"tid":447862,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成日整喊女朋友 點算好？","createTime":"2017-10-25T16:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T03:50:06.000Z","uid":63989,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0aad6062bf2078041903b5c6757acd9f67cf5820","tid":447862,"uid":63989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"我女朋友連續3日都比我整喊，我應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n早兩日佢比左個fd 張相我睇，問我正唔正，我話正佢就開始喊，話驚我會鐘意第二個靚女。<br />\n琴晚佢就發現我ig有follow d j 圖，又嬲到喊。<br />\n啱啱我同fd食飯少左覆佢wtsapp，佢又喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地日日朝早下就都好開心咁拍下拖咁，但係到咗夜晚就有野整喊佢，點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係好愛佢，唔想佢成日喊，有冇巴打教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa93c5d8004e79a448e840e8c6d9b8c6367be23","tid":447862,"uid":66283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"d749b6cb5c56af1af60af105d6433852c71b57e5","tid":447862,"uid":63989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手</blockquote><br />\n仲有咩方法"},{"pid":"be02bad9bcfbcd4c1a952fbe9eb9b98b3dc7aeb7","tid":447862,"uid":88306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分手</blockquote><br />\n仲有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵第2個"},{"pid":"2b7902528a59f9a51fc22c9d8ff93aa436fb2638","tid":447862,"uid":100052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"佢係咪準備嚟m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 荷爾蒙失調姐"},{"pid":"b93a1a07b3bef9b871d06391af3a9b8e5122a927","tid":447862,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25